Description:
     xpd is designed to provide an  easy-to-use,  point-and-click
     interface  to a correlation of process information available
     through ps.

Instilation:
     See INSTALL file

Platforms:
     This software was written and tested on a Sun Sparc X running 
     SunOS 4.1.3.

Contact:
     Vincent M. Tkac
     vmtkac@acm.org

Last Updated:
     March 1994
     Updates will be posted to ftp.x.org.

For more information see man page and TeX manual.